      <p>Two days isn't a long time, all three of the developers involved had some ideas about how the service could be improved over time. Below are some highlights.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The ability for a user to request a company sign up.</li>
        <li>More in depth data about the company</li>
        <li>More news sources and social proof of the company</li>
        <li>A crowd sourced approval process, giving additional agency for a company's mission statement.</li>
        <li>More clients, iOS and Android</li>
